?1 dialogs

The following dialogs pop up at the center of the screen and block everything
until dealt with.
@hsee
SymChooser , dialog#VBox
@h
? boolean_dialog
@hsyn
 boolean_dialog("@varlabel", ["@varaccept", "@varcancel"])
@hdesc
	return 1 or 0
@h

? continue_dialog
@hsyn
 continue_dialog("@varlabel")
@hdesc
	info to the user
@h

? string_dialog
@hsyn
 string_dialog("@varlabel", @varstrdef)
@hdesc
	returns 0 if canceled and @varstrdef remains unchanged
@h
